data.description: Beautiful turnkey single home with POOL. Completely remodeled! Situated on a corner lot has everything that all the buyers are looking for. Almost $300K in renovations, including a brand new Pool with heater, new roof, new oversized driveway, new everything! This home has many great bonuses including new perimeter aluminum fence with a 12ft gate, new oversized screened patio terrace, new minigolf and isolated pergola. Featuring new modern appliances, new interior glass barn doors, impact windows and doors, new controlled blinds, freshly painted, new glass wine cellar, new closets, new laundry and with new washer and dryer. All the lights are controlled by smart switches. Smart locks for all the exterior doors, new sprinkler system and pump, new landscape. Close to everything! LOCATION!
